係達文西最出名嘅作品。但係大家又知唔知，呢兩幅名畫令世人讚嘆嘅地方究竟係邊度？而達文西又係喺咩環境之下創作佢地呢？<br />\n一連兩集歷史二三事：<br />\n《尋找名畫蒙羅麗莎》《尋找名畫最後的晚餐》有 Ben Sir 帶大家發掘呢兩幅名畫背後嘅秘密！<br />\n#bensir<br />\n<br />\n雙語廣播：粵語/英語 (電視版)<br />\n播放頻道：港台電視 31<br />\n播出時間：<br />\n(首播) 2021年3月23、30日 星期二晚上9時30分<br />\n(重溫) 2021年3月24、31日 星期三 凌晨12時及中午12時<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/historyontuesdays\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhistoryontuesdays&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=32edc847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/historyontuesdays</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/31seetheworld/videos/281745600134819/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F31seetheworld%2Fvideos%2F281745600134819%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=0a55b468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/31seetheworld/videos/281745600134819/</a>"},{"pid":"e758c88556b98bfc43b7de6d9c559c2dd561c006","tid":2439770,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"最快推爆係歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc75a59d0a12bb29262a202aba7f59ec922f491","tid":2439770,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7452a2a67d8e4d98950877e5067bedcb4f5f98fd","tid":2439770,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed8b557ba9e560558f009451d5e9c8d730eceba","tid":2439770,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:21:56.000Z","msg":"好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"呢個規模要去到一千年之後先有其他城市追得到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"君士坦丁堡：<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041505